== Exponent ==

Exponentiation is defined using [/edit/peano/peano_thms.gh/df-exponent | repeated multiplication ].

=== Properties ===

* Power of 0: [/edit/peano/peano_thms.gh/exp0 | A^0 = 1]
* Identity: [/edit/peano/peano_thms.gh/expid | A^1 = A]
* Addition: [/edit/peano/peano_thms.gh/expadd | A^(B+C) = A^B ∙ A^C	]
* Multiplication: [/edit/peano/peano_thms.gh/expmul | (A∙B)^C = A^C ∙ B^C	]
* Exponent: [/edit/peano/peano_thms.gh/expexp | (A^B)^C = A^(B∙C)	]

